 extra metadata hidden in them, prior to sharing on social media. This ensures your proprietary workflows and system information are not also shared accidentally.\n\n**Workflow Creator:** [ultimo_intento](https://civitai.com/user/ultimo_intento)\n\n**MetaWipe Repo:** [Github](https://github.com/UltimateIntent/ComfyUI-MetaWipe.git)\n\n**View Metadata**       \n- Link folder path or filepath(s) to Metawipe Metadata Inspector\n- Individual file metadata can be reviewed by selecting files from dropdown\n  - Set Recursive: true to include subfolders\n  - Output links can view all info for entire folder\n\n**Wipe Metadata**\n- Link image, video, audio, folder path or filepath(s) to Metawipe (All-in-One)\n  - Set Recursive: true to include subfolders\n  - Output links can view all info for entire folder\n\n**Save Generated Media Without Metadata**\n- Supports all media types\n- Can support passthrough to regular save node\n\nFile save location\n\n```\nComfyUI/\n├───📂 output/\n│   ├───📂 [folder-name]/\n        └─── [prefix][original-filename]\n"],"color":"#222","bgcolor":"#000"},{"id":118,"type":"LoadVideo","pos":[-1969.389030893813,2647.94802636361],"size":[482.64187923430563,471.19177391230505],"flags":{},"order":9,"mode":4,"inputs":[{"localized_name":"file","name":"file","type":"COMBO","widget":{"name":"file"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"choose file to upload","name":"upload","type":"IMAGEUPLOAD","widget":{"name":"upload"},"link":null}],"outputs":[{"localized_name":"VIDEO","name":"VIDEO","type":"VIDEO","links":[254]}],"properties":{"ue_properties":{"widget_ue_connectable":{},"input_ue_unconnectable":{}},"cnr_id":"comfy-core","ver":"0.21.1"},"widgets_values":["AnimateDiff_00034.mp4","image"]},{"id":117,"type":"MetaWipeAllInOne","pos":[-2436.8440268418426,3271.090423659077],"size":[293.08203125,126],"flags":{},"order":12,"mode":4,"inputs":[{"localized_name":"any_input","name":"any_input","type":"*","link":252},{"localized_name":"output_subfolder","name":"output_subfold